DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
LENEGHAN 2016-0370 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 11, 2018

DISCIPLINARY CASE

On petition for reinstatement by respondent, Patrick Peter Leneghan, Attorney Registration No. 0041931, last known address in Brooklyn Heights, Ohio. Petition granted. Patrick Peter Leneghan reinstated to the practice of law in Ohio.
